------------------------Version5 With Anjaly joy-------------------------------

Context--

The Kingdom of Balloria is known for its wizards and their colorful magical balls.
    These balls are very powerful and have to be stored safely when not in use.

Requirements-
    As provider of a service that lets wizards store their balls.
    I'd like a bag that can hold a maximum of 12 balls.


    Ballorian law is very strict about the placement of balls.
